{"tid":1793064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警犬所搜獲之手槍為P80 (即glock17)手槍, AR-15步槍，為香港特警廣泛使用","createTime":"2019-12-22T05:54:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T03:23:13.000Z","uid":188176,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"030433b4ad08b41d2df0c5157cc8c8ae7c65cf5e","tid":1793064,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T05:54:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/1281/%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%AD%B8%E9%99%A2%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE%E6%97%A5-%E6%A7%8D%E6%A2%B0%E8%A3%9D%E5%82%99%E5%A4%A7%E6%99%92%E5%86%B7-glock-17%E5%BD%88%E5%8C%A3%E5%AE%B9%E9%87%8F%E5%A4%A7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F1281%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E9%2599%25A2%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2594%25BE%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E6%25A7%258D%25E6%25A2%25B0%25E8%25A3%259D%25E5%2582%2599%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2599%2592%25E5%2586%25B7-glock-17%25E5%25BD%2588%25E5%258C%25A3%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E9%2587%258F%25E5%25A4%25A7&d=QEbR3JiquQCbCEiBABctD4tKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=0099ecf9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/1281/%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%AD%B8%E9%99%A2%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE%E6%97%A5-%E6%A7%8D%E6%A2%B0%E8%A3%9D%E5%82%99%E5%A4%A7%E6%99%92%E5%86%B7-glock-17%E5%BD%88%E5%8C%A3%E5%AE%B9%E9%87%8F%E5%A4%A7</a><br />\n<br />\n而<span style=\"color: red;\">Glock 17半自動手槍（Glock 17, Pistol）</span>由奧地利葛洛克有限公司生產，是目前全球執法單位使用最多的手槍之一，口徑9毫米，重620克，槍管長114毫米，總長度185毫米，標準彈匣為17發，<span style=\"color: red;\">由特別任務連（俗稱飛虎隊）、機場特警、反恐特勤隊、保護要員組（俗稱G4）、保護證人組及水警小艇分區配備。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">P80咪即係Glock，有乜分別</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1791490/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1791490/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/oLHVmww.png\" />"},{"pid":"a4294ce27937dec6a081279b29dcb6e48d63d9c8","tid":1793064,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T05:55:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">AR15來福槍</span>（AR 15, Rifle）在美國曲特製造公司生產，5.56毫米口徑，重2.95千克，槍管長508毫米，長度達990毫米，可容納20發子彈，<span style=\"color: red;\">為內部保安大隊及特定單位人員配備武器</span>。"},{"pid":"243609994fc3714222ecd96c620fb06bc3791f18","tid":1793064,"uid":188176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T05:57:49.000Z","msg":"【大埔開槍案】警拘 19 歲男子 疑與北角槍械案有關 檢 AR-15 長距離步槍及手槍 過二百發子彈<br />\n<br />\n大埔昨晚有人向警方開槍，警方拘捕一名 19 歲男子，在現場檢獲一枝 <span style=\"color: red;\">P 80 手槍</span>，並在附近一個單位檢獲一枝，和警方使用同型號的<span style=\"color: red;\"> AR 15</span> 步槍，和逾 200 發子彈，該男子涉嫌非法管有槍械被捕；警方初步相信，案件和月初警方在北角檢獲真槍和大量子彈的案件有關，懷疑疑犯計劃在公眾活動中開槍襲擊警員。<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%94%E9%96%8B%E6%A7%8D%E6%A1%88-%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%98-19-%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90-%E7%96%91%E8%88%87%E5%8C%97%E8%A7%92%E6%A7%8D%E6%A2%B0%E6%A1%88%E6%9C%89%E9%97%9C-%E6%AA%A2-ar-15-%E9%95%B7%E8%B7%9D%E9%9B%A2%E6%AD%A5%E6%A7%8D%E5%8F%8A%E6%89%8B%E6%A7%8D-%E9%81%8E%E4%BA%8C%E7%99%BE%E7%99%BC%E5%AD%90%E5%BD%88/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259F%2594%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%25A7%258D%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%258B%2598-19-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590-%25E7%2596%2591%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%258C%2597%25E8%25A7%2592%25E6%25A7%258D%25E6%25A2%25B0%25E6%25A1%2588%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%2597%259C-%25E6%25AA%25A2-ar-15-%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%25B7%259D%25E9%259B%25A2%25E6%25AD%25A5%25E6%25A7%258D%25E5%258F%258A%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A7%258D-%25E9%2581%258E%25E4%25BA%258C%25E7%2599%25BE%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25BD%2588%2F&d=QEbR3JiquQCbCEiBABctD4tKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=1b92f256\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259F%2594%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%25A7%258D%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%258B%2598-19-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590-%25E7%2596%2591%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%258C%2597%25E8%25A7%2592%25E6%25A7%258D%25E6%25A2%25B0%25E6%25A1%2588%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%2597%259C-%25E6%25AA%25A2-ar-15-%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%25B7%259D%25E9%259B%25A2%25E6%25AD%25A5%25E6%25A7%258D%25E5%258F%258A%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A7%258D-%25E9%2581%258E%25E4%25BA%258C%25E7%2599%25BE%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25BD%2588%2F&h=790d9c4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%94%E9%96%8B%E6%A7%8D%E6%A1%88-%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%98-19-%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90-%E7%96%91%E8%88%87%E5%8C%97%E8%A7%92%E6%A7%8D%E6%A2%B0%E6%A1%88%E6%9C%89%E9%97%9C-%E6%AA%A2-ar-15-%E9%95%B7%E8%B7%9D%E9%9B%A2%E6%AD%A5%E6%A7%8D%E5%8F%8A%E6%89%8B%E6%A7%8D-%E9%81%8E%E4%BA%8C%E7%99%BE%E7%99%BC%E5%AD%90%E5%BD%88/</a><br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"f3852b668a85f86037811d68881d0cc4e08e22ce","tid":1793064,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T05:59:23.000Z","msg":"有組織罪案及三合會調查科高級警司李桂華稱，警方前晚根據情報到場截停目標人物，<span style=\"color: red;\">其間對方從腰間拿出半自動步槍並開了一槍</span>，沒擊中人，被探員制服。他指出，警方持法庭手令到翠屏花園一個單位搜捕，發現一支AR15步槍，內有211發子彈，其中有61發在環形快速入彈器中，其他子彈分別在5個彈匣內。警方並檢獲一支P80型號手槍，於屋內及現場發現44發中空子彈，並尋獲相信是開槍後的彈殼。"},{"pid":"1effa72be7820bed39f8a51a0581eba9012e6c3c","tid":1793064,"uid":78154,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T06:00:38.000Z","msg":"如果係手足有門路拎到就振奮人心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c556cbfe971641ae90d0080a4678da3b3d4a61ca","tid":1793064,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T06:01:52.000Z","msg":"根據警犬所言,涉事之被捕人從腰間拿出半自動步槍,但影片所見地上之槍械為手槍,而彈頭為警方廣泛使用之9mm 子彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=12&amp;v=NEZ9kaEIPno&amp;feature=emb_logo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D12%26v%3DNEZ9kaEIPno%26f